<p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">秋意渐浓，时光正好。近日，B250510班的同学们迎来了一场别开生面的秋日团建。这是一次青春的相聚，更是一次心灵的靠近。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>才艺秀场：青春就要闪闪发光</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967787106.png" alt="1765967787106.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967787106.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">当音乐响起，舞台属于每一个勇敢展示的同学。动感的舞步诠释着青春的活力，清澈的歌声唱出年轻的心声。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967811420.png" alt="1765967811420.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967811420.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967824611.png" alt="1765967824611.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967824611.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">在这里，我们看到了课堂之外那个多才多艺的你，也感受到了集体温暖的力量。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967836235.png" alt="1765967836235.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967836235.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>美食时光：香气四溢的欢乐共享</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967856725.png" alt="1765967856725.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967856725.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">精心准备的各色烤串香气扑鼻，为活动现场增添了别样的温暖。同学们围坐在一起，享受着美味可口的烤串和零食，分享着生活中的趣事。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967881390.png" alt="1765967881390.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967881390.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967901543.png" alt="1765967901543.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967901543.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">一串串香气四溢的美食，不仅满足了味蕾，更串起了彼此的情谊，让这个秋日的相聚倍显温馨。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967928056.png" alt="1765967928056.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967928056.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>游戏时光：笑声是最美的乐章</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967953119.png" alt="1765967953119.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967953119.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">"击鼓传花"让每个人都成为焦点，即兴表演展现真实自我；"谁是卧底"考验智慧与默契，欢声笑语中拉近彼此距离。而"你画我猜"环节更是妙趣横生，抽象的图画、夸张的比划引发阵阵笑声，简单的游戏却让我们看到了彼此最可爱的模样。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967965797.png" alt="1765967965797.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967965797.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967999368.png" alt="1765967999368.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765967999368.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765968009170.png" alt="1765968009170.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765968009170.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">令人惊喜的是，老师们也加入了这场青春派对。讲台上严肃认真的他们，此刻却和我们一起欢笑歌唱，共享美食。在轻松愉快的氛围中，老师们和同学们畅谈生活，分享经历，这份亦师亦友的情谊，成为这个秋天最珍贵的礼物。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765968019951.png" alt="1765968019951.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765968019951.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765968045207.png" alt="1765968045207.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765968045207.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>以青春之名，赴未来之约</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">这个秋日，我们不仅收获了欢笑，更收获了彼此。从初识的拘谨到如今的默契，从独立的个体到温暖的集体，B250510班正在书写属于我们的青春故事。愿这份美好延续，愿我们的情谊在时光中沉淀，在岁月里芬芳。未来的日子，让我们继续携手，在这个温暖的大家庭里，共同成长，彼此照亮。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765968057179.png" alt="1765968057179.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765968057179.png" style="width: 50%;"></p>